<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:28:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国外长会见印度外长呼吁恢复直航</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</link><description>中国外交部周二发表声明称，中国外交部长王毅周一在里约热内卢会见了印度外长苏杰生，并呼吁恢复两国之间的直航。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-meets-indian-counterpart-calls-resumption-direct-flights-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨，美元走弱，因美国国债收益率下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-19/</link><description>亚洲股市周二上涨，而美国债券收益率和美元则从数月高点回落，交易员等待当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的内阁选择，并试图评估美联储宽松的前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院判处民主活动人士戴耀廷10年监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentences-pro-democracy-activist-benny-tai-10-years-prison-2024-11-19/</link><description>香港高等法院周二在长达数年的国家安全审判中判处一名主要民主活动人士入狱十年，该审判损害了香港一度活跃的民主运动，并引起了全球批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentences-pro-democracy-activist-benny-tai-10-years-prison-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>常德小学外发生车祸 多名学生受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/multiple-students-injured-outside-primary-school-chinas-changde-says-state-media-2024-11-19/</link><description>《环球时报》在推文中称，周二上午，湖南省常德市一所小学外发生车祸，造成多名学生受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 02:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/multiple-students-injured-outside-primary-school-chinas-changde-says-state-media-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>条款清单显示，阿里巴巴公布了 50 亿美元双币债券的初步价格指导</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/alibaba-delivers-initial-price-guidance-5-billion-dual-currency-bond-term-sheet-2024-11-19/</link><description>根据路透社周二审阅的一份条款清单，阿里巴巴集团已向投资者提供了其 50 亿美元双币债券的初步价格指导。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 01:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/alibaba-delivers-initial-price-guidance-5-billion-dual-currency-bond-term-sheet-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港在具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中监禁了45名民主活动人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hundreds-queue-sentencing-47-hong-kong-democrats-2024-11-19/</link><description>被贴上“组织者”标签的前法律学者戴耀廷被判处十年监禁。刑期从四年多到十年不等。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 01:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hundreds-queue-sentencing-47-hong-kong-democrats-2024-11-19/</guid></item><item><title>习近平希望同墨西哥继续交往、推进合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-wants-continue-exchanges-advance-cooperation-with-mexico-2024-11-18/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周二报道，中国国家主席习近平表示，中墨要继续加强交往，重续友谊，发挥好两国经济互补性强的特点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 23:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-wants-continue-exchanges-advance-cooperation-with-mexico-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>苏里南财政部长表示与中国签署债务重组协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/suriname-signs-debt-rescheduling-with-china-finance-minister-says-2024-11-18/</link><description>苏里南财政部长斯坦利·拉霍巴尔辛周一在国民议会上表示，苏里南与中国签署了债务重组协议，该南美国家债务管理办公室负责人表示，今年将首次向债权人还款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 22:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/suriname-signs-debt-rescheduling-with-china-finance-minister-says-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国快递集团顺丰控股将在香港上市筹集至多7.927亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sf-holding-raise-7927-mln-its-hk-ipo-2024-11-18/</link><description>中国最大的快递公司顺丰控股周二表示，计划在香港上市筹集至多61.7亿港元（合7.9271亿美元），这是香港资本市场复苏的最新迹象。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 22:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sf-holding-raise-7927-mln-its-hk-ipo-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院小组将就涉嫌中国黑客事件举行听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-senate-panel-hold-hearing-chinese-hacking-incidents-2024-11-18/</link><description>美国参议院司法委员会负责技术问题的小组委员会将于周二就中国黑客事件举行听证会，其中包括最近涉及美国电信公司的事件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 22:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-senate-panel-hold-hearing-chinese-hacking-incidents-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：寻求全球指引，观察美联储钟摆的摆动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 21:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国习近平告诉 G20 峰会 人工智能不应该是“富裕国家的游戏”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-tells-g20-summit-ai-should-not-be-game-rich-countries-xinhua-reports-2024-11-18/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周一报道，中国国家主席习近平在里约热内卢举行的二十国集团峰会上警告说，人工智能不应该成为“富裕国家和富人的游戏”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 21:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-tells-g20-summit-ai-should-not-be-game-rich-countries-xinhua-reports-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>德国肖尔茨将与中国习近平讨论俄罗斯无人机问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germanys-scholz-address-drones-russia-with-chinas-xi-2024-11-18/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周一表示，在有报道称一家中国工厂正在为俄罗斯生产军用无人机后，他将在 G20 峰会上与中国国家主席习近平讨论军民两用物资的交付问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germanys-scholz-address-drones-russia-with-chinas-xi-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德在中国推出肥胖药物Wegovy</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-has-launched-obesity-drug-wegovy-china-2024-11-18/</link><description>诺和诺德周一表示，已在中国推出广受欢迎的肥胖药物Wegovy。中国是全球第二大药品市场，估计中国有超过1.8亿人患有肥胖症。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 13:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-has-launched-obesity-drug-wegovy-china-2024-11-18/</guid></item><item><title>需求激增，小米再次提高电动汽车交付目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-posts-jump-third-quarter-revenue-beats-estimates-2024-11-18/</link><description>中国小米公司周一表示，今年的目标是交付 13 万辆电动汽车，第三次提高了预期，这家汽车制造商新贵第三季度收入增长了 30.5%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-posts-jump-third-quarter-revenue-beats-estimates-2024-11-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>